WildFires & Smoke Signs of Last Days: Lot's Wife In Gomorrah, Country Living, Mark of The Beast & People Suffering From PTSD.

 In this episode, Andrew Henriques addressed the Canadian Wild Fires & Smoke Polluting the air & water supply of 17 States in the U.S. The presentation revealed the spiritual and practical preparation necessary to meet these crises that will precede the Second Coming of Jesus.
